Package: libgtkflow-0.8-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: devhelp
Description: Documentation for libgtkflow-0.8
 This package contains a devhelp-book that holds API
 documentation for libgtkflow. The devhelp-book can
 be read via the software devhelp.

Package: libgtkflow-0.8-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgtkflow-0.8-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends},
         libglib2.0-dev,
         libgtk-3-dev,
         libc6-dev,
         libgflow-0.8-dev,
         libcairo2-dev,
         gir1.2-gtkflow-0.8
Description: Flow graph library for Gtk+-3.0 headerfiles
 This package contains development headerfiles for the 
 flow-graph-library libgtkflow. It contains c-headers 
 and vapi-files.

Package: gir1.2-gtkflow-0.8
Section: introspection
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${gir:Depends}
Description: Typelib (gobject-introspection)-files for libgtkflow
 This package contains gobject-introspection files for libgtkflow
 With these files, programmers can use libgflow through the
 gobject-introspection of various scripting-languages like e.g.
 Python, Perl, Lua, PHP, JS and more

