Package: libgtkflow-0.8-1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgflow-0.8-1, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Flow graph library for Gtk+-3.0
 This library provides an additional Gtk3-Widget that
 allows the drawing and manipulation of the data-flow-
 models provided by libgflow.

Package: libgflow-0.8-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgflow-0.8-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends},
         libglib2.0-dev,
         libc6-dev,
         gir1.2-gflow-0.2
Description: Data flow modeling library headerfiles
 This library provides development headers for libgflow
 It contains typelib-files for gobject-introspection,
 c-headers and vapi-files.

Package: gir1.2-gflow-0.8
Section: introspection
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${gir:Depends}
Description: Typelib (gobject-introspection)-files for libgflow
