Package: libgflow-0.8-1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Description: Data flow modeling library based on glib
 This library allows application developer to design
 data flow models. These models know units that create,
 transform or consume data. These nodes can be
 programmmatically interconnected thus forming flow-models.
